"&kicker; is the &kde; application starter panel and is also capable of some "
"useful applets and extensions. It usually resides on the bottom of the "
"desktop."
msgstr ""
"&kicker; es el panel &kde; iniciador de aplicaciones y también es capaz de "
"applets útiles y extensiones. Normalmente reside en la parte inferior del "
"escritorio."

